Text: Mailafternoon Mary I work in the San Francisco Enron office and we have received some mail addressed to you Both envelopes have the same return address of Spiegel McDiarmid New York Avenue NW Washington DC I tried to locate your address on People Finder but didnt have much luck If you could email or call me with your location I could forward these on to you Thanks Jennifer Lind
